                    <span>Overall this book gives a good overview and lots of useful information. It could use some updating to accommodate for the current market.<P>The samples are helpful and can be modified to meet one's needs.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good basic stuff although a bit dated</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
